OL,3,CPep Guardiola to leave Man City at end
OL,4,Cof the season, ITV News understands
OL,6,FThe players have known for some time
OL,7,Fnow, and there were clues everywhere:
OL,8,FPep Guardiola's repeated non-denials
OL,9,Fwhen quizzed about his future, and the
OL,10,Fdisappearance of some coaching staff
OL,11,Ffor new challenges.
OL,13,FEven Manchester City fans at the FA
OL,14,FCup final sensed something was up.
OL,16,FGuardiola has changed his mind before,
OL,17,Fbut ITV News understands this is
OL,18,Fdefinitely it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
