OL,3,CPep Guardiola to leave Man City at end
OL,4,Cof the season, ITV News understands
OL,6,FThe two-year contract he signed a year
OL,7,Fago now seems a useful PR smokescreen.
OL,8,FThis was always the plan.
OL,10,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,11,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,12,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,13,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,15,FThe club would not confirm reports on
OL,16,FMonday night that the 55-year-old
OL,17,FCatalan would take charge for the
OL,18,Ffinal time on Sunday against Aston
OL,19,FVilla, but I understand they are
OL,20,Fpreparing for his departure.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
