OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1779289870
OL,3,CPep Guardiola to leave Man City at end
OL,4,Cof the season, ITV News understands
OL,6,FGuardiola led City to six Premier
OL,7,FLeague and one Champions League
OL,8,Ftitles, not to mention three FA Cups.
OL,10,FWhether Pep's departure is confirmed
OL,11,Fbefore the end of the season is
OL,12,Fsomething the club must be wrestling
OL,13,Fwith now, but the timing of the
OL,14,Fspeculation is not helpful, given
OL,15,Fthere are three important points at
OL,16,Fstake at Bournemouth tonight, if City
OL,17,Fare going to have any chance of
OL,18,Fsnatching the Premier League title
OL,19,Ffrom Arsenal on the final day.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/4
